    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上汇聚，两个节点都指向\"More Questions?\"判断。然后Yes分支回到\"Display Question\"形成循环，No分支到\"End Game\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
