    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我刚才说错了。让我确认一下——\"Is Answer Correct?\"的Yes和No标签，以及\"More Questions?\"的Yes和No标签，都要标注清楚，别搞混了。",
      "elements_involved": [
